snippet.title: Armchair Detective, BLUE
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Armchair Detective Channel.  True Crime & other Case Mysteries. 
Join me as I dissect the cases that have baffled the public over the years. 
All my videos are based on the research of myself and my amazing team.
I have a private Facebook Group and we have a members only Patreon Group.
Please like, subscribe, and click the notification bell follow us and keep updated.
I have provided the links for everything down below.
Thank You
AD
